subsection_name: roi-loan-phan-ly.json_3_Effects of dissociative disorders on life and health
subsection_content:
If left untreated, possible effects on a person with dissociative disorder may include:
Difficulties in life such as relationships, jobs...; Having sleep problems such as insomnia; Sexual problems; Depression; Anxiety disorders; Eating disorder; Self-harm, even suicide
